	<h1 class="title">这个音乐软件什么来头，测试版上线3天就被三大唱片公司告了？</h1>
	<div class="author-date clearfix">					
			<div class="author clearfix">
					<span class="avatar x25 circle">
						<img src="/system/users/faces/102277/small/102277.jpg?1432868256" alt="">
					</span>
				<span class="name">韩方航 </span>
			</div>
		<span class="date smart-date" data-originDate="2015-10-14 12:57:15 +0800"></span>
	</div>
	<div class="banner">
			<img src="/system/articles/articleshows/16076/medium/16076.jpg?1444797826" alt="" />			
	</div>
	<!-- 传入参数：obj(aritcle, paper, card, mob) -->


<div class="com-share" data-id="16076" data-title="《这个音乐软件什么来头，测试版上线3天就被三大唱片公司告了？》，来自@好奇心日报" data-pic="http://www.qdaily.com/system/articles/articleshows/16076/medium/16076.jpg?1444797826" data-url="http://www.qdaily.com/mobile/articles/16076.html" data-weiboAppkey="2462590045">
